{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 308099, "create_time": 1658476860, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "不一定理想？", "timestamp": 1658476860}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 308100, "create_time": 1658477013, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "不一定可逆", "timestamp": 1658477013}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 308101, "create_time": 1658477066, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 这个等式对于是否可逆都是成立的", "timestamp": 1658477066}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 308102, "create_time": 1658477087, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "话说，为啥我输入的第一个公式是斜体，后面不是？", "timestamp": 1658477087}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 308105, "create_time": 1658477312, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re 洞主: 原来是用成了中文输入英文，$dG=0$", "timestamp": 1658477312}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 308113, "create_time": 1658477919, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "发生化学反应的话，化学式会变吧，你这个式子是系统组成不变的时候的热力学基本关系，组成变化要加上化学式那一项", "timestamp": 1658477919}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 308126, "create_time": 1658478368, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 嗯我知道，你说的是 $dG=-SdT+VdP+\\mu dn$，但最后一项为什么一定要小于0", "timestamp": 1658478368}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 308129, "create_time": 1658478561, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 适用范围是封闭系统、无非体积功、可逆；如果不可逆需要设计可逆路径", "timestamp": 1658478561}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 308132, "create_time": 1658478609, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "是由dG小于0推出来的化学势降低吧", "timestamp": 1658478609}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 308150, "create_time": 1658479666, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Dave: D君对应用条件的解释是正确的，而dz最开始的理解有一点点偏差。\n具体而言（以下记系统对外做功为正）：\n1. 对于封闭系统，有dU=δQ-δW（热力学第一定律）；\n2. 若过程可逆，则δQ=TdS（熵的定义）；\n3. 若不做非体积功，则δW=pdV（体积功公式）；\n4. 2, 3代入1得dU=TdS-pdV；\n5. 由Gibbs自由能定义，G=A+pV，两侧取全微分再带入4得dG=Vdp-SdT。\n\n因此，严格地说，最后一个式子至少有封闭系统、可逆、无非体积功三个适用条件，参见朱文涛《基础物理化学（上册）》pp.94-95。", "timestamp": 1658479666}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 308154, "create_time": 1658479751, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 不对吧，G是状态量，跟过程无关，无论是否可逆，给定两个状态，G的变化就是相同的。", "timestamp": 1658479751}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 308158, "create_time": 1658479869, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 推到过程确实要求可逆，但事实上这个等式不需要可逆为条件，假设一个不可逆过程，但你知道了始末状态，那么你可以沿着可逆过程定义这个dG", "timestamp": 1658479869}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 308159, "create_time": 1658479871, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "虽然无关，但还是想说一下，微分符号是\\mathrm d哦！$\\mathrm d$ 和$d$不太一样～", "timestamp": 1658479871}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 308162, "create_time": 1658480023, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: dz说得很对，那样就是【设计】了一个可逆过程，所以“严格地说”才需要可逆条件，事实上可以用在不可逆的情况。不过封闭和无非体积功两个条件是跑不掉的，如果涉及到化学反应、张力等还会更麻烦。", "timestamp": 1658480023}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 308168, "create_time": 1658480129, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 我很明白这个过程，但我想不明白的是，对于等温等压系统，我告诉你两个状态，那么这两个状态的dG是不是就是0", "timestamp": 1658480129}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 308169, "create_time": 1658480158, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 谢谢，长教训了", "timestamp": 1658480158}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 308191, "create_time": 1658480799, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 我的理解是，对于一个封闭的等温等压系统（事实上这种限制下可供发生的改变已经很少了），如果仅经历简单物理过程（排除化学/生物学反应、电热、表面张力等），那么dG恒等于0，如dz所说的那样", "timestamp": 1658480799}], "create_time": 1658476790, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1658578898, "likenum": 7, "n_attentions": 7, "n_comments": 17, "pid": 86959, "poll": null, "reply": 17, "text": "$dG =-SdT+VdP$ 对于定温定压系统，吉布斯自由能不是不变吗？也就是$dG＝0$，为何教材上会说对于定温定压系统 $dG≤0$", "timestamp": 1658476790}}